            <!-- Tour Description -->
            <div class="tour-description">
                <h2>Experience the Magic of a Camel Ride in Agadir at Sunset</h2>
                <p>Embark on an unforgettable <strong>sunset camel ride Agadir</strong> adventure that combines the romance of traditional Moroccan transportation with the spectacular beauty of the Atlantic coastline. This <strong>camel ride on the beach Agadir</strong> experience offers the perfect way to watch the sun dip below the horizon while gently swaying on camelback along pristine golden sands.</p>
                
                <p>Your <strong>Agadir camel riding tour</strong> begins with convenient hotel pickup, taking you to the beautiful beach area where our gentle, well-trained camels await. As the golden hour approaches, you'll mount your camel and begin a peaceful journey along the shoreline, with the sound of waves and the warm glow of sunset creating an atmosphere of pure magic.</p>
                
                <p>This isn't just a <strong>camel ride in Agadir</strong> ‚Äì it's a complete cultural experience! After your scenic beach ride, you'll be welcomed into a traditional Berber tent where authentic Moroccan hospitality awaits. The evening continues with a delicious BBQ dinner featuring grilled meats, fresh salads, traditional bread, and seasonal fruits, all while enjoying traditional Berber music and entertainment.</p>

                <h3>What Makes This Camel Ride and BBQ Agadir Experience Special?</h3>
                <p>Unlike rushed tourist activities, our <strong>sunset camel ride Agadir</strong> experience is designed to give you authentic moments and lasting memories. We keep our groups small (maximum 12 people) to ensure personalized attention from our experienced guides and handlers. Our camels are well-cared for, gentle, and perfect even for first-time riders.</p>
                
                <p>The timing of our tour is carefully chosen to coincide with the most beautiful light of the day. As you ride along the beach, you'll witness the sky transform into brilliant shades of orange, pink, and purple ‚Äì creating perfect photo opportunities that will make your Instagram followers jealous! Our guides know exactly where to stop for the best sunset views and are happy to take photos of you and your group.</p>
                
                <p>Whether you're a couple seeking a romantic experience, a family looking for a unique adventure, or friends wanting to try something authentically Moroccan, this <strong>camel ride on the beach Agadir</strong> is perfect for all ages and fitness levels. No riding experience is necessary ‚Äì our patient camel handlers will ensure you feel comfortable and safe throughout the entire journey.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Detailed Itinerary -->
            <div class="itinerary-section">
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937; margin-bottom: 30px;">Detailed Itinerary: Your Sunset Camel Ride & BBQ Experience</h2>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">5:00 PM - 5:30 PM (Summer) / 4:00 PM - 4:30 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Hotel Pickup in Agadir or Taghazout</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">We'll collect you from your hotel or riad in Agadir, Taghazout, or surrounding areas in a comfortable, air-conditioned vehicle. Your professional driver will greet you and provide an overview of the evening ahead. Pickup time varies by season to ensure perfect sunset timing.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">5:30 PM - 6:00 PM (Summer) / 4:30 PM - 5:00 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Arrival at Beach & Meet Your Camel</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Arrive at the pristine beach location where our gentle, well-cared-for camels await. Meet your experienced camel handler who will introduce you to your camel and help you mount safely. Don't worry ‚Äì our camels are calm, friendly, and perfect for beginners! Get comfortable in the saddle and prepare for an unforgettable experience. Your guide will explain basic riding instructions and safety guidelines.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">6:00 PM - 7:00 PM (Summer) / 5:00 PM - 6:00 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Magical Sunset Camel Ride Along the Beach</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Begin your enchanting camel ride along Agadir's beautiful coastline. Feel the gentle sway of your camel's gait as you ride along the golden sands with the Atlantic Ocean beside you. Watch as the sun begins its descent, painting the sky in brilliant shades of orange, pink, and purple. Your guide will stop at the perfect spots for photos ‚Äì capture stunning silhouettes of camels against the sunset! This peaceful one-hour ride allows you to truly connect with this ancient mode of transportation while enjoying one of nature's most beautiful spectacles. Listen to the sound of waves, feel the sea breeze, and create memories that will last a lifetime.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">7:00 PM - 7:30 PM (Summer) / 6:00 PM - 6:30 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Traditional Mint Tea Ceremony</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">After your camel ride, you'll be welcomed into a traditional Berber tent set up on the beach. Experience authentic Moroccan hospitality with a traditional mint tea ceremony. Learn about the cultural significance of mint tea in Moroccan life while enjoying the sweet, refreshing beverage. This is a wonderful opportunity to relax, share stories with fellow travelers, and immerse yourself in Berber culture. Your guide will explain the tea-making tradition and answer any questions about Moroccan customs.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">7:30 PM - 8:30 PM (Summer) / 6:30 PM - 7:30 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Authentic Moroccan BBQ Dinner</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Feast on a delicious traditional Moroccan BBQ dinner prepared fresh on the beach. The menu includes succulent grilled meats (chicken, beef, or lamb), fresh Moroccan salads, warm bread straight from the oven, seasonal fruits, and traditional side dishes. Vegetarian options are available upon request. Enjoy your meal in the Berber tent while being entertained by traditional Berber music. The combination of great food, beautiful setting, and cultural entertainment creates a truly magical evening experience.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">8:30 PM - 9:00 PM (Summer) / 7:30 PM - 8:00 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Entertainment & Relaxation</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">After dinner, enjoy traditional Berber music and entertainment around a campfire (weather permitting). This is a perfect time to relax, take final photos under the stars, and soak in the peaceful beach atmosphere. Some evenings may include traditional drumming demonstrations or folk music performances. Simply sit back, enjoy the moment, and savor the end of a perfect Moroccan evening.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">9:00 PM - 9:30 PM (Summer) / 8:00 PM - 8:30 PM (Winter)</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Return Transfer to Your Hotel</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">After this unforgettable evening, your driver will return you safely to your hotel in Agadir or Taghazout. Relax in the comfortable vehicle as you reflect on the magical camel ride and authentic Moroccan experience you just enjoyed. Your guide will be happy to provide recommendations for other activities and attractions in Agadir.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

